            <p>Please note that the informations returned from the data methods are just informations.
They do not show or mark if a locale exists or not.</p>

<p>When you are missing a locale for San Marino as mentioned by you, then add an issue within CLDR (<a href="http://cldr.unicode.org">http://cldr.unicode.org</a>).</p>

<p>Note: Even the latest CLDR release 1.9 does not have a locale for San Marino.</p>

